tourBios.carHigh:
2015: Easily qualified for the PGA TOUR China Series' season, with a runner-up finish at the Mainland China Qualifying Tournament in early March at Wolong Lake GC in Liuzhou. Despite the high finish, still ended the tournament a distant seven shots behind medalist Wen Yi Huang. 

2014: Shot rounds of 75-75 at the Lanhai Open outside Shanghai to miss the cut in his PGA TOUR China Series debut.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA Tour China Serie was T22nd in 2015 at the The Eternal Courtyard Open.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T59th in Total Birdies on the PGA Tour China Series.
